    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS darrija\n/ un fohti warren dauds Kuk-\niu nabze Waraüś Namma/un\nnna Kalpo Namma / un wiṣ-\nEgiptes-Semmê/ un ta Sem-\ntappe maitata no teem Kuk-\nxeem.\n"
