      "text": "Tad aizinaja Waraüś\nobsu un Aāronu / un ẜazzija:\nta / un uppurejeet juhsu Dee-\num (teju) Semmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Mohsus ẜazzija : tas\nirr pareisi/ ta darriht/ jo mehs\nytum to Egipteru Negantibu\nnKUNGAM muhsuDeewam\npurejscht. Redsi/ ja tad mehs\nEgipteru Negantibu winxo\nceeffchā uppuretum/neggi tec\nhs ar Aknixeem nomehtatu ?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mehs ectim kahdn treijo\neno Gahjumu Tuksnefi / un\npuretim tam KUNGAM\nthfu Deewam / itt ka winscb\nmums irr ẜazzijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad ẜazzija Waraüś: Es\nmaidischu juhs / ka juhs tan\nURNSAM juhsuDeewam war-\nt uppureht/ tikkai jums ne buhs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ẜazzija Mohsus:\nRaugi es eetnu no tewig nohst/\nun luhgſchu to KUNGII / ka\nſcheem Kukkaineem rihtu buhs at-\nkahpt no Waraüś/ un no winxa\nKalpeein/ un no winxa Laudim/\ntikkai Waraüm ne buhs wairs\nmanni peetwilt / tohs Laudis ne\natlaidams / ka tee tam KUN-\nGAM warr uppureht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad isgahje Mohsus no\nWaraüś/ un luhdse to KUNGII\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS darrija\npehz Mohsus Wahrda / un tee\nKukkaini atkahpe no Waraüś/ un\nno winxa Laudim/ ka tur ne\nweens palikke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr Waraüś ir scho\nBrihdi fawu Sirōt apzeetinaja/\nun ne atlaidē tohs Laudis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad ẜazzija tas KUNGS\nus Mohsu: Eij pee Wa-\nraüś/ un runna us to:\nTa fakka tas KUNGS / to Ee-\nbreezu Deews: Atlaid mannuš\nLaudis/ ka tee man kalpo;\n"
    },
